data.description: This beautiful split level home sits on a quiet dead end street. The kitchen and living room has new luxury vinyl plank flooring. The kitchen has been upgraded with new countertops and newly painted cabinets. Low maintenance metal roof, double carport, single garage building, and a single garage in the basement. Large bonus room that can be used as a 4th bedroom, bonus room, man cave, or office space. New windows throughout the house in 2021. HVAC/heat pump 2018. Tons of storage space! No HOA!!
